        <ArticleTitle>A Course-Based Undergraduate Research Experience (CURE) in Biology: Developing Systems Thinking through Field Experiences in Restoration Ecology.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>ar20</StartPage>
          <MedlinePgn>ar20</MedlinePgn>
